subject: America''s Cup
Sailboats and Sailing
lead_paragraph: The legal duel between Ernesto Bertarelli of Alinghi and Larry Ellison of BMW Oracle Racing is still unresolved and the America's Cup showfown between the two, scheduled for Valencia on Feb. 8, is in doubt.
